         <abstract id="aspace_0df8d81f448af9b342410763a6e6d732">The records consist of correspondence, memoranda, and reports documenting the activities and operations of the Office of Educational Research at Yale. Materials include correspondence concerning appointments, terminations and finances, Yale College faculty reports, reports done for the State of Connecticut, and College Entrance Examination Board files.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <corpname identifier="dts_a1bc0560f0d1d7a4717b1206e4023f38f2dda6d0" source="naf">
               <part>Yale University. Office of Educational Research</part>
            </corpname>
         </origination>
    
